org.jbei.ice.lib.models

Class Sequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.lib.models.Sequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IDataModel

    @Entity
public class Sequence
extends Object
implements IDataModel
    Stores the unique sequence for an Entry object.

    • sequence: Normalized (lower cased, trimmed) sequence for Entry.
    • sequenceUser: Original sequence uploaded by the user. For example, the unparsed genbank file, if that was the original upload. If the original upload does not exist, then this field is the same as sequence.
    • fwdHash, revHash: sha1 hash of the normalized sequence for fast searches.
    • sequenceFeatures: SequenceFeature objects.
    Author:
    Timothy Ham, Zinovii Dmytriv
